social_posts.post_text:
So... if you guys haven't noticed, we're launching a new YouTube Channel called @birthdayseries. It's a passion project we've been building for the last year, and it's finally coming to life. 

The concept is very simple: in each episode, a guest makes an actionable wish from their bucket list, and we bring it to life. Subscribe or you’re dead to us! The first episode launches August 13th.

We wouldn’t be here today without an incredible group of quality humans supporting us, especially our production team & videographers/editors! 🎂 🎈 

#birthdayseries #vlogseries #lightthecandle

We can’t wait to make some waves with episode #001 of @birthdayseries which goes live August 6th

Every episode will feature a guest with an actionable bucket list item or “birthday wish”. Once they blow out the candle, @birthdayseries serves as the forcing function to bring the idea to life. 

A lot of our friends told us turn on the cameras and hit publish as soon as possible, but we knew that if we were patient enough to build this slowly we could put ourselves in a position to be consistent and grow in a more strategic way. We have six long form episodes in the bank with a few hundred short form pieces of content ahead of the launch. Laying the foundation for this channel has been a surfing expedition in itself with its ups and downs; we have a new found respect for content creators.

Subscribe via our ‘link in bio’ & come along 
for the ride, it’s going to be a fun one! 🎂🎈
